            "populationDescription": "All patients (pts) who initiated first-line (1L) pembrolizumab and platinum-based combination chemotherapy (CT) after 1st June 2018, and subsequently discontinued 1L therapy and had started second-line treatment with afatinib at least 3 months prior to date of data collection. Only afatinib treated patients with an EGFR mutation positive or negative status were included in the analysis.",
