      "descriptionModule": {
        "briefSummary": "The purpose of this study is to evaluate the antitumor effects of sotorasib and RMC-4630 in subjects with KRASG12C mutant NSCLC",
        "detailedDescription": "This is a phase 2 multicenter, open-label study evaluating the efficacy, safety, tolerability, and pharmacokinetics (PK) of RMC-4630 in combination with sotorasib in subjects with KRASG12C mutant NSCLC after failure of prior standard therapies."
      },
